'''Domenico Neziti''' (born [[May 9]]th, [[1971]]) was the colorist for the [[Star Wars comic books|comics]] [[Empire 38|''Empire'' 38]]
and [[Empire 39|''Empire'' 39]].

Born in Toronto, he now lives in Italy and is a comic book artist as well as an illustrator and concept artist. He also works as a colorist for the French comic industry.

